  "notes": "## Mahnwesen (Dunning)\n\n### Setup Required\n1. **Credentials**: Set up 'Supabase API' and 'OpenAI API Key' in n8n.\n2. **GoCardless**: Set GOCARDLESS_ACCESS_TOKEN and GOCARDLESS_ACCOUNT_ID env vars. Register at bankaccountdata.gocardless.com.\n3. **PDF Service**: Set PDF_GENERATION_WEBHOOK_URL env var pointing to your PDF gen service.\n4. **Supabase invoices table**: Must have columns: status, due_date, invoice_number, invoice_date, total, iban, customer_id, dunning_level, dunning_pdf_url, dunning_sent_at, days_overdue, paid_date, payment_transaction_id.\n\n### Dunning Levels\n- < 14 days: Zahlungserinnerung (gentle reminder)\n- 14-30 days: 1. Mahnung (first notice)\n- 30-60 days: 2. Mahnung (second notice)\n- > 60 days: Letzte Mahnung vor Inkasso (final notice before collections)"
}
